{"parentUuid":"c630e593-764d-433c-b634-ab1072130679","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"bcf5258e-2708-4b49-a1f7-27fad0c3c471","agentId":"a70f09b91abb2edaa","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MtzdK4AiPCFxmAorSxRNNQ","type":"tool_result","content":"=== secrets.get_database_url ===\n1:\"\"\"Runtime secrets facade — the only module that talks to AWS Secrets Manager / SSM.\n3:Business logic never calls `boto3` or reads a secret value from `os.environ`\n33:    environment-variable fallback for local development.\n66:            value = os.environ.get(env_fallback)\n70:                f\"or the '{env_fallback}' environment fallback\"\n78:        so local/dev environments without AWS credentials can fall back.\"\"\"\n83:        return response.get(\"SecretString\")\n94:def get_database_url() -> str:\n\n=== deploy.yml migrate DATABASE_URL resolution ===\n14:      - name: Snapshot BEFORE migrate (backup-before-migrate, executable)\n16:          SNAP=\"pre-migrate-$SHA-$(date -u +%Y%m%d%H%M%S)\"\n20:      - name: Migrate staging (expand/contract enforced upstream by plan-audit)\n22:          DATABASE_URL=\"$(aws ssm get-parameter --with-decryption --name <STAGING_DB_URL_SSM> --query Parameter.Value --output text)\"\n23:          [ -n \"$DATABASE_URL\" ] && [ \"$DATABASE_URL\" != \"None\" ] || { echo \"staging DB URL not resolved from SSM — refusing to migrate\" >&2; exit 1; }\n24:          export DATABASE_URL\n25:          <MIGRATE_CMD>\n70:      - name: Snapshot BEFORE migrate (prod)\n72:          SNAP=\"pre-migrate-$SHA-$(date -u +%Y%m%d%H%M%S)\"\n75:      - name: Migrate prod\n77:          DATABASE_URL=\"$(aws ssm get-parameter --with-decryption --name <PROD_DB_URL_SSM> --query Parameter.Value --output text)\"\n78:          [ -n \"$DATABASE_URL\" ] && [ \"$DATABASE_URL\" != \"None\" ] || { echo \"prod DB URL not resolved from SSM — refusing to migrate\" >&2; exit 1; }\n79:          export DATABASE_URL\n80:          <MIGRATE_CMD>","is_error